summary: Dark Ink Art are having a mystery tube sale! Each tube costs $60 and contains 4 prints including an exclusive 'K'2SO' screen...
caption:
Dark Ink Art are having a mystery tube sale!

Each tube costs $60 and contains 4 prints including an exclusive ‘K'2SO’ screen print by Brian Miller, as well as randomly selected prints that could include art from 'Star Wars’, 'Indiana Jones’, 'Alien’, Firefly’, 'The Simpsons’ and more

The sale starts Thursday November 29 at 9am PT from the Dark Ink Art website.

blog.description:
He/Him, Cis, Gay, British, Old fart, Probably not as cynical as appears

Mostly comics, with mutant/technorganic selfsoulfriends and swashbuckling, acrobatic (and frequently imperilled) heroes as specialities,

Also cartoons, toys, anime and whatever else catches my eye.

Basic rule - Don't be a dick... unless you can be Dick Grayson, in which case be Dick Grayson because, paradoxically, he wouldn't be a dick,
